https://www.gardewilson.com.au/#)Close ContactOpen Contact\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nLocations:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nMelbourne\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBrisbane / Gold Coast\n\n\n[book an appointment](https://calendly.com/gardewilsonlawyers)\n\n## MELBOURNE’S\n\n## MELBOURNE’S leading\n\n# Melbourne's Best Criminal Defence Lawyers\n\nAggressive Defence For When You’ve Been\n\nCharged With A Criminal Offence.\n\nBOOK AN APPOINTMENT\n\nFREE CASE ASSESSMENT\n\n[CALL 24/7 - 0400002188](tel:0400 002 188)\n\nWe’re featured on:\n\n![Scrolling Image](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/garde_wilson_is_featured_in_these_sites.webp)\n\n![zarah garde wilson](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\nWe’re featured on:\n\n![Scrolling Image](<Base64-Image-Removed>)\n\n![zarah garde wilson](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/zarah-whole-body-2.webp)\n\n## Are you a first time offender?\n\nAsk us how we can keep your record clean.\n\nfind out more\n\n## EXPERTISE\n\n## Engage with Melbourne's  Best Criminal Lawyers\n\n[01\\\\\n\\\\\n**Drug Possession / Trafficking**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nOffences involving illegal drugs or\\\\\n\\\\\ncontrolled substances.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/drug-possession-trafficking/) [02\\\\\n\\\\\n**traffic charges**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nYour best chance at keeping your\\\\\nlicence or getting it back fast.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/traffic-lawyers/) [03\\\\\n\\\\\n**Drug Driving**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nDriving a motor vehicle while under the influence of drugs or alcohol to the degree.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/drug-driving-lawyers/) [04\\\\\n\\\\\n**Crypto Currency**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nIt imposes stringent reporting and registration obligations on digital currency exchange providers.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/crypto-currency-offences-and-laws/) [05\\\\\n\\\\\n**War Crimes**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nThis includes prohibitions against intentionally targeting civilians, inflicting unnecessary suffering.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/war-crimes/) [06\\\\\n\\\\\n**Extradition Laws and defence**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nLegal mechanism by which one nation transfers an individual to another for criminal prosecution.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/extradition-laws-and-defence/) [07\\\\\n\\\\\n**INTERPOL Red Notices**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nServes as the primary liaison between that country’s law enforcement and INTERPOL.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/interpol-red-notices/) [08\\\\\n\\\\\n**Drink Driving**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nPeople caught on numerous occasions driving motor vehicle over the prescribed blood alcohol limit.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/drink-driving-lawyers/) [09\\\\\n\\\\\n**Assault charges**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nActs of physical harm or threats against another person.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/assault-lawyers/) [10\\\\\n\\\\\n**Family Violence**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nBehaviour by a person towards another person with whom the first person is in a relevant relationship.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/family-violence-lawyers-in-melbourne/) [11\\\\\n\\\\\n**Weapons Firearms**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nOffences involving the illegal use or possession of weapons.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/weapons-firearms/) [12\\\\\n\\\\\n**Fraud & theft**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nDeceptive acts for financial or personal gain.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/fraud-theft/) [13\\\\\n\\\\\n**bail**\\\\\n\\\\\n![Defences list](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/arrow-gold-4.svg)\\\\\n\\\\\nTemporary release of an individual who has allegedly committed an offence for the duration between being arrested and charged and their proceeding court date.](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/offences/bail/)\n\n## Need to Contact a   Loved One in Custody?\n\nIf you or a loved one is being held in custody anywhere in Greater Melbourne or across Victoria, Garde Wilson Lawyers can provide rapid representation and expert advice to take on your fight for justice.\n\nget in touch\n\n## TESTIMONIALS\n\n## What Our   Clients  Are Saying?\n\n## What Our Client Are Saying?\n\n[![testmonials](https://www.gardewilson.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/google-logo.png)](https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=d425b5dac0dba72a&cs=0&si=APYL9bs7Hg2KMLB-4tSoTdxuOx8BdRvHbByC_AuVpNyh0x2KzTOGNBq2bNt0r93V8P0p9Gulbd3v8N6wK5E_BZGDcb71rqiedqE7ZlQM2_6iUHqMAXJ2_wUyVmn4Dl27LJsg4YxKgVfOOxK-Zn-ifvSn9s10DSpYew%3D%3D&q=Garde+Wilson+Criminal+Lawyers+Reviews&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjn1ePx3YOMAxUwr1YBHQ9yOrsQ0bkNegQILBAE&biw=1440&bih=677&dpr=2)\n\n[Google Reviews](https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=d425b5dac0dba72a&cs=0&si=APYL9bs7Hg2KMLB-4tSoTdxuOx8BdRvHbByC_AuVpNyh0x2KzTOGNBq2bNt0r93V8P0p9Gulbd3v8N6wK5E_BZGDcb71rqiedqE7ZlQM2_6iUHqMAXJ2_wUyVmn4Dl27LJsg4YxKgVfOOxK-Zn-